FBIS4-43180 "drweu114_j_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-114 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Occhetto Comments Occhetto Comments LD1306141894 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1343 GMT 13 Jun 94 LD1306141894 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Text] Achille Occhetto has resigned as secretary of the Democratic Party of the Left [PDS] in a letter to Giglia Tedesco, the chairman of the party's commission. "I want to avoid groundless objections and controversy by submitting my resignation," Occhetto wrote. "My decision is not capitulation, but an act of pride and struggle in the name of the PDS and the Left."
